                </p>
                <p id="pg_3">
                    Stanislas initiated the scientific research on electrochemistry and antiox measurement to develop a
                    skincare prescription tool, and launched a first B2C sun prevention tool (mapo solar).
                </p>
                <p id="pg_4">
                    Stanislas initiated the scientific research on electrochemistry and antiox measurement to develop a
                    skincare prescription tool, and launched a first B2C sun prevention tool (mapo solar).
                </p>
                <div class="mt-5 float-end">
